'''Steven Staley''' ([[10 March|March 10]], [[1963]]) is an American voice actor who works primarily in the anime circuit. He voiced [[Frodo Baggins]] and [[Celeborn]] in the game ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring (video game)|The Fellowship of the Ring]]'' and did additional voices for ''[[The Hobbit (2003 video game)|The Hobbit]]''.
